article: the american institute in taiwan -lrb- ait -rrb- and the u.s. department of energy -lrb- doe -rrb- will hold an opening ceremony on wednesday to officially launch the unk initiative in which cargo at southern taiwan 's port of kaohsiung will be screened to prevent the smuggling of material used to make weapons of mass destruction .
